FBIS4-9176 "dreeu078_y_94008" FBIS-EEU-94-078 Daily Report 21 Apr 1994 YUGOSLAVIA Kosovo Serbs Deploy Troops Near Kosovo-Albanian Border Serbs Deploy Troops Near Kosovo-Albanian Border AU2104203794 Pristina KOSOVA DAILY REPORT Nr. 340 in English 21 Apr 94 AU2104203794 Pristina KOSOVA DAILY REPORT Nr. 340 English BFN [Unattributed report: "Additional Serbian Army Forces Deployed in Dragas"] [Text] Alongside with the frequent movements of the Serbian army throughout Kosova, additional units of these forces have been recently deployed in the areas adjacent to Albania. Today's BUJKU reports that over the last couple of days several additional units of the Serbian army have been brought in the military barracks in Dragas (town near the Kosovo-Albania border). As reported, the Serbian army has recently commenced to amend and repair the military barracks near the border, which have not been used for decades.
